PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774433137
OL,3,CMarried At First Sight relationship
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling dies aged 54
OL,6,F"In her final moments, when I thought
OL,7,Fcancer had taken away her ability to
OL,8,Fspeak, she ushered me closer and
OL,9,Fwhispered a message for Maddie and me
OL,10,Fthat will sustain me for the rest of
OL,11,Fmy life.
OL,13,F"It took all of her remaining
OL,14,Fstrength, and that gesture summed up
OL,15,Four wee Melsie perfectly.
OL,17,F"Even then, her only thought was for
OL,18,FMaddie and me. This is a woman who
OL,19,Fbecame a new mum and a TV star at 42 `
OL,20,Fand nailed both.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774433137
OL,3,CMarried At First Sight relationship
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling dies aged 54
OL,6,F"This is a woman who, through two
OL,7,Fyears of chemotherapy, when she could
OL,8,Fbarely lift her head from the pillow,
OL,9,Fnever complained and never stopped
OL,10,Fshowing courage, grace, compassion and
OL,11,Fempathy, and never missed a day of
OL,12,Ffilming.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,F"To most of you, she was Mel Schilling
OL,20,F` matriarch of MAFS and queen of
OL,21,Freality TV.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774433137
OL,3,CMarried At First Sight relationship
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling dies aged 54
OL,6,F"To Maddie and me, she was our wee
OL,7,FMelsie: an incredible mum, role model,
OL,8,Fand soulmate.
OL,10,F"On behalf of our family and her
OL,11,Fincredible friendship group, thank you
OL,12,Ffor the support from around the world."
OL,14,FThe statement continued: "Life can be
OL,15,Fbeautiful, and life can be incredibly
OL,16,Fcruel. But ultimately, life is
OL,17,Ffleeting, fragile, and tomorrow is
OL,18,Fpromised to no one.
OL,26,@vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
