PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774433137
OL,3,CMarried At First Sight relationship
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling dies aged 54
OL,6,F"If you can do anything to honour Mel,
OL,7,Fplease live life to the full, love
OL,8,Fyour people well, and try not to sweat
OL,9,Fthe small stuff.
OL,11,F"I had 15 wonderful years with my
OL,12,Fsoulmate, and it was the privilege of
OL,13,Fmy life to be by her side. For that, I
OL,14,Fwill be forever thankful.
OL,16,F"Goodbye, my love. My one. Until we
OL,17,Fmeet again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
