OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774433137
OL,3,CMarried At First Sight relationship
OL,4,Ccoach Mel Schilling dies aged 54
OL,6,FSchilling had previously announced she
OL,7,Fwould be stepping back from the
OL,8,FAustralian version of the programme
OL,9,Fafter 12 seasons on the expert panel.
OL,11,FChannel 4 paid tribute to the
OL,12,Frelationship coach, in a statement
OL,13,Fshared on Instagram, describing
OL,14,FSchilling as someone who "radiated
OL,15,Fjoy, warmth and optimism".
OL,17,FThe statement said: "We're privileged
OL,18,Fto be the channel that is home to
OL,19,FMel's work, which was at the heart of
OL,20,FMarried At First Sight's phenomenal
OL,21,Fsuccess, both in the UK and Australia.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
